DS18B20example3.sch demonstrates temperature measurement with DS18B20 sensor using DS18S20Library and Atmega32 microcontroller.

The temperature reading from the sensor is presented on a two line LCD module with HD44780 driver.

The software part is listed in DS18B20Example3.c source file.

The schema is created wiht Eagle 7.3.0.  

